    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Not sure if this can be of any use, but in the ongoing vue.js implementation we offer the ability to \"freeze\" the sync with Algolia so that multiple SearchParameters can be mutated without triggering a search query for each.\r\n\r\nAlso as long as the helper doesn't trigger a `change` event, we don't trigger new search queries.\r\n\r\ni'd gladly discuss this specific point if needed.",
